  "instructions": [
    "Heat the sesame oil in a small saucepan over low heat.",
    "Add the ginger paste and cook for 1 minute, stirring constantly.",
    "Stir in the peanut butter until smooth and creamy.",
    "Add the dashi extract, honey, and salt. Whisk until well combined.",
    "Pour the mixture into a donabe or small saucepan.",
    "Bring the mixture to a gentle simmer over low heat.",
    "Steam the mixture for 5 minutes, or until heated through.",
    "Garnish with sliced scallions and fresh mint sprigs.",
    "Serve immediately, hot or warm.",
    "Garnish with additional scallions and mint if desired."
